rComments: Used to be uninteresting for the first semester, after that she became much more enthusiastic and lively. Great lecturer, knows her material inside out, very calm and helpful to students. And yes, she's a pretty cute prof!

Tough marker but great lecturer.  Attendance to tutorials was mandatory and you had to write a response to the reading every week, but it wasn't too hard.  Oh, and she is so hot!  Just checking her out was half the reason I went to class.  If I was single, I totally would've asked her out!
Very helpful professor and a great lecturer! She's super funny and explains things quite well. Not to mention she's VERY easy on the eyes.
